1. *Vjeruješ* li mi da sam vidjela duha sinoć? (Do you believe me that I saw a ghost last night?)
2. Da *vjeruješ* u sebe, možeš postići sve što poželiš. (If you believe in yourself, you can achieve anything you want.)
3. Oni *vjeruju* u drugačije vrijednosti i način života od nas. (They believe in different values and way of life than us.)
4. *Vjerujući* da će sve biti u redu, odlučio sam napustiti posao. (Believing that everything will be alright, I decided to quit my job.)
5. Ne *vjerujem* da ćemo stići na vrijeme na koncert ako ne krenemo sada. (I don't believe we will make it to the concert on time if we don't leave now.)
6. *Vjerovao* sam da si drugačiji od ostalih, ali očigledno sam se prevario. (I believed you were different from others, but obviously I was wrong.)
7. Kad bih *vjerovao* u horoskope, ne bih ništa poduzimao jer mi piše da je danas loš dan. (If I believed in horoscopes, I wouldn't do anything because it says today is a bad day.)
8. Nikada ne bih *vjerovao* da ćeš me tako izdati. (I would have never believed you would betray me like that.)